      "arraySize": 1,
      "dimensions": 1,
      "description": "sqrt - Square  of Input 1. abs - Absolute Value of Input 1. sign - Sign of Input 1. cos - Cosine of Input 1. sin - Sine of Input 1. tan - Tangent of Input 1. acos - Arccosine of Input 1. asin - Arcsine of Input 1. atan - Arctan of Input 1. atan2 - Arctan of (Input 1 / Input 2). cosh - Hyperbolic Cosine of Input 1. sinh - Hyperbolic Sine of Input 1. tanh - Hyperbolic Tangent of Input 1. log - Log base 10 of Input 1. logb - Log base Base Value of Input 1. ln - Natural Log of Input 1. pow10 - 10 to the power of Input 1. exp - e to the power of Input 1. powe - Base value to the power of Input 1. If Base value is negative result is -((-Base Value) ^ Input 1) powb - Input 1 to the power of Exponent value.  If Input 1 is negative result is -((-Input 1) ^ Exponent Value). pow - ((-Input 1) ^ Input 2) dbtopower - Decibel (Input 1) to amplitude. powertodb - Amplitude (Input 1) to decibel. dbtoamp - Decibel (Input 1) to amplitude. amptodb - Amplitude (Input 1) to decibel.",
      "tooltip": "",
      "help": "",
